data.description: This beautiful home is sure to impress! Boasting 3 bedrooms, 2 full bathrooms. You will love the open floor plan and neutral finishes. The combined kitchen/dining area is low-maintenance and opens up to the living room, creating the perfect spot to entertain. Relaxing will be a breeze on the back patio that overlooks the spacious fenced-in backyard. . Within close reach to Topsail Beaches, Stone Bay and Camp Lejeune. Come envision your new beginning while it's still available! Home sells with a 210 Home Warranty.
